name: Deepsea Engulfer
text:
Flood {1}{g}{g}{g}({1}{g}{g}{g}, Exile this card from your hand: Target land loses all land types and abilities and has "{T}: Add {c}." Flood only as a sorcery.) 
Whenever you flood Deepsea Engulfer or it enters the battlefield, destroy target artifact or echantment an opponent controls.
